dc_description_s: This file geodatabase contains parcel data including plat boundaries, tax parcels, easements and road right of ways. Attributed Parcel Point and Polygon data represent property descriptions (legal descriptions) and land ownership in Ramsey County joined to tax parcels. The following links can be used to obtain individual metadata pages: Attributed Parcel Point: plan_attributedparcelpoint.html Attributed Parcel Poly: plan_attributedparcelpoly.html Common Interest: plan_commoninterest.html Subdivision: plan_subdivision.html Tax Parcels: plan_taxparcel.html Conveyance Division: plan_conveyancedivision.html Special Survey: plan_specialsurvey.html Parcel Info: plan_parcelinfo.html Easement: plan_easement.html Landtie: plan_landtie.html Right of Way: plan_rightofway.html Historic Right of Way: plan_historicrightofway.html
